Class PyJavaDictionary

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class PyJavaDictionary
extends org.python.core.PyDictionary

Exposes an unmodifiable java.util.Map as a public field directly accessible from Jython. The map reflects changes made through the PyDictionary methods.

See Also:
Map, Serialized Form
